label s1
"You are relaxing in a trophy room. It's comfortable but the shelves would look much better with treasure on them. The door leads north." 0

label s2
"You are just north of a small brick building. There is a forested path to the north. A rough gravel road leads east." 0

label s3
"You are following an east/west gravel road. There is literally nothing of interest here. You vow to keep walking until you find somewhere better." 0

label s4
"You have reached a clearing in the forest. A steep path leads north and south." 0 

label s5
"You are at the top of a tree covered hill. A rugged trail descends to the south. In the distance you can see what appears to be a cave entrance. A golden eagle has made its nest here." 0 

label s6
"The east/west road is muddy here, but otherwise remains completely boring." 0

label s7
"A nondescript road stretches west from here. Much more exciting is a cave entrance to the south." 0

label s8
"You scramble over dimly lit boulders to a chamber where you can almost stand. Passages lead off in all directions." 0

label s9
"A stream emerges from the surface here, carving passages to the south and west. A crampt crawlway goes east." 0

label s10
"You are in an awkward sloping east/west canyon." 0

label s11
"You are in a little twisty maze of passages." 0

label s12
"Someone has been here. The rocks are coated with a thin layer of soot. You spot an empty can of beans and an old shoe. A crumpled note in the shoe reads \"The road is more interesting than it seems. Go north.\" A small crevice leads back north." 0

label s13
"You are in a twisting maze of passages." 0

label s14
"You are on an overgrown trail. A clear path leads south, and a very confusing path leads north." 0

label s15
"You stumble into a small clearing. An obscure trail leads west. Off to one side you spot the remains of a hobo campsite. Tacked to a tree is a note saying \"Good job\"" 0

label s16
"You are in a twisty maze of little passages." 0

label s17
"You are in a twisty little maze of passages." 0

label s18
"You are in a maze of little twisting passages." 0

label s19
"You are in a crampt chamber full of stalactites. A pile of bones from some unfortunate creature lies in the corner." 0 

label s20
"You are in a splendid chamber 50 feet high. An ornate and very locked doorway leads north, while small passages continue south and east. A fire breathing dragon guards the room! Luckily he looks friendly." 0

label s21
"You discover a vault full of treasures! Paintings, antiques, gold, and diamonds line the room. As a treasure expert, you unfortunately realize they're all elaborate fakes. You angrily punch through a \"priceless painting\" to discover a secret passageway leading north." 0 

label s22
"To your surprise, you find a clean and organized room full of computer equipment. It looks as if someone has been here recently. Filing cabinets neatly adorn the walls, along with a circuit diagram for an 8-bit carry lookahead adder." 0 

label s23
"A natural fountain bubbles up from the floor here. A cool breeze chills the air. Small passages you can barely fit through branch off to the north and south." 0 
