label s41
"Welcome to Smol Cave Adventure! You are a daring explorer in search of fame and fortune. Your mission, should you choose to accept it, is to recover the legendary treasures from the Smol Cave system nearby.\nMake sure to turn on the keyboard, then press n,s,e,w to move. Press i to view your inventory. Good luck!" 0

label s42
"Try as you might, you can't go that direction." 0

