label s49
"As you return to the trophy room, a wave of accomplishment washes over you. You have braved the legendary Smol Cave. You defeated the fire breathing dragon (kind of). You place your trophies on the shelves and think of what to do next...\nSuddenly you have an idea. You sit down at your computer and install Turing Complete 1.0. You start building something awesome. What will it be?\nThanks for playing!" 0